data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning single-family home is located in the desirable Augustus Pass neighborhood of New Braunfels. With 4 spacious bedrooms and an open floor plan, this property offers ample space for your family to grow and thrive.  The large island in the kitchen is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying a cozy family meal. The carpet and laminate flooring add warmth and comfort throughout the livable area, which measures a generous 1888 sq ft.  Situated on a .124-acre lot, this home boasts a gas neighborhood with breathtaking views from the back porch. The central air conditioning, ceiling fans, and gas heating ensure year-round comfort.  Built with quality construction materials such as wood and brick, this house exudes durability and charm. The roof is made of durable shingles that will protect your investment for years to come.  Convenience is key with off-street parking for two vehicles and an HOA that takes care of community maintenance for only $88 per quarter.  Enjoy the convenience of having a laundry room inside your home as well as window blinds already installed.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a beautiful family home in New Braunfels. Call today to schedule a viewing!
